statement: select a.k3||':'||b.k4 as col1,sum(a.k6+b.k6) as col2 from aggregate_tbl a inner join unique_par_tbl partition(p202008) b on a.k12 = b.k12 and a.k9 = b.k9 where a.k3 like(with tbl1 as  (select distinct k3 from duplicate_tbl),  tbl2 as  (select distinct k3 from aggregate_par_tbl partition(p202006) where k4 not in('futian','baiyun','luohu'))  select * from tbl1 where k3 <>(select * from tbl2 order by 1 nulls last limit 1)  order by 1 limit 1)  and a.k13 >= 0  and b.k5 is not null  group by 1 order by 2 desc,1;
